====
Bugs
====

Report a bug by adding a link to a page describing it. Please specify the git
hash of the commit the bug refers to.

- There is a race condition in the L1 spike delivery. We need to ensure updates
  to s_current are serialised. We cannot directly use atomic floating point
  additions for this purpose,  but we should be able to use integer atomics to
  implement a per-target neuron lock facility.
- OutOfBoundsNeuronIndexCrash
- HaskellRandomisation
